text: To Wong Foo, Thanks for Everything! Julie Newmar is a 1995 American road comedy movie directed by Beeban Kidron and starring Wesley Snipes, Patrick Swayze, Stockard Channing, John Leguizamo, Blythe Danner, Chris Penn, Arliss Howard, Mike Hodge. It was distributed by TriStar Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * * * Category:1995 comedy movies Category:1995 LGBT movies Category:1990s buddy movies Category:1990s road movies Category:American comedy movies Category:American LGBT movies Category:American road movies Category:Movies directed by Beeban Kidron Category:Movies set in the United States
